{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":991,"text":"Imagine that you are a product designer."},{"time":4686,"text":"And you've designed a product,"},{"time":6156,"text":"a new type of product,\ncalled the human immune system."},{"time":11161,"text":"You're pitching this product"},{"time":12650,"text":"to a skeptical, strictly\nno-nonsense manager."},{"time":16378,"text":"Let's call him Bob."},{"time":17848,"text":"I think we all know\nat least one Bob, right?"},{"time":21542,"text":"How would that go?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":23925,"text":"Bob, I've got this incredible idea"},{"time":25981,"text":"for a completely new type\nof personal health product."},{"time":28637,"text":"It's called the human immune system."},{"time":31447,"text":"I can see from your face that\nyou're having some problems with this."},{"time":34700,"text":"Don't worry. I know it's very complicated."},{"time":36800,"text":"I don't want to take you\nthrough the gory details,"},{"time":39481,"text":"I just want to tell you about some\nof the amazing features of this product."},{"time":43733,"text":"First of all, it cleverly uses redundancy"},{"time":46686,"text":"by having millions of copies\nof each component --"},{"time":49842,"text":"leukocytes, white blood cells --"},{"time":52051,"text":"before they're actually needed,"},{"time":53825,"text":"to create a massive buffer\nagainst the unexpected."},{"time":58276,"text":"And it cleverly leverages diversity"},{"time":61660,"text":"by having not just leukocytes\nbut B cells, T cells,"},{"time":65405,"text":"natural killer cells, antibodies."},{"time":67943,"text":"The components don't really matter."},{"time":69669,"text":"The point is that together,"},{"time":71263,"text":"this diversity of different approaches\ncan cope with more or less anything"},{"time":75903,"text":"that evolution has been able to throw up."},{"time":79933,"text":"And the design is completely modular."},{"time":83860,"text":"You have the surface barrier\nof the human skin,"},{"time":87173,"text":"you have the very rapidly reacting\ninnate immune system"},{"time":90418,"text":"and then you have the highly targeted\nadaptive immune system."},{"time":95017,"text":"The point is, that if one system fails,\nanother can take over,"},{"time":98886,"text":"creating a virtually foolproof system."}]},{"cues":[{"time":103170,"text":"I can see I'm losing you, Bob,\nbut stay with me,"},{"time":105485,"text":"because here is the really killer feature."},{"time":109773,"text":"The product is completely adaptive."},{"time":112789,"text":"It's able to actually develop\ntargeted antibodies"},{"time":117355,"text":"to threats that it's never\neven met before."},{"time":120680,"text":"It actually also does this\nwith incredible prudence,"},{"time":125081,"text":"detecting and reacting\nto every tiny threat,"},{"time":129203,"text":"and furthermore, remembering\nevery previous threat,"},{"time":133562,"text":"in case they are ever encountered again."},{"time":136624,"text":"What I'm pitching you today\nis actually not a stand-alone product."},{"time":141569,"text":"The product is embedded\nin the larger system of the human body,"},{"time":146008,"text":"and it works in complete harmony\nwith that system,"},{"time":148945,"text":"to create this unprecedented level\nof biological protection."},{"time":152023,"text":"So Bob, just tell me honestly,\nwhat do you think of my product?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":156342,"text":"And Bob may say something like,"},{"time":158890,"text":"I sincerely appreciate\nthe effort and passion"},{"time":161829,"text":"that have gone into your presentation,"},{"time":164696,"text":"blah blah blah --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":165874,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":167078,"text":"But honestly, it's total nonsense."},{"time":172081,"text":"You seem to be saying that the key\nselling points of your product"},{"time":175474,"text":"are that it is inefficient and complex."},{"time":178760,"text":"Didn't they teach you 80-20?"},{"time":181693,"text":"And furthermore, you're saying\nthat this product is siloed."},{"time":185676,"text":"It overreacts,"},{"time":187105,"text":"makes things up as it goes along"},{"time":188668,"text":"and is actually designed\nfor somebody else's benefit."},{"time":191183,"text":"I'm sorry to break it to you,\nbut I don't think this one is a winner."}]},{"cues":[{"time":195267,"text":"If we went with Bob's philosophy,"},{"time":197237,"text":"I think we'd actually end up\nwith a more efficient immune system."},{"time":200729,"text":"And efficiency is always important\nin the short term."},{"time":204875,"text":"Less complex, more efficient,\nmore bang for the buck."},{"time":208322,"text":"Who could say no to that?"},{"time":210151,"text":"Unfortunately, there's one\nvery tiny problem,"},{"time":212562,"text":"and that is that the user\nof this product, you or I,"},{"time":215851,"text":"would probably die\nwithin one week of the next winter,"},{"time":219548,"text":"when we encountered a new strain\nof the influenza virus."}]},{"cues":[{"time":225191,"text":"I first became interested\nin biology and business,"},{"time":229385,"text":"and longevity and resilience,"},{"time":231788,"text":"when I was asked a very unusual question"},{"time":234063,"text":"by the CEO of a global tech company."},{"time":237257,"text":"And the question was:"},{"time":238731,"text":"What do we have to do to make sure\nthat our company lasts 100 years?"},{"time":246811,"text":"A seemingly innocent question,"},{"time":248405,"text":"but actually, it's a little trickier\nthan you might think,"},{"time":252341,"text":"considering that the average\nUS public company now"},{"time":256591,"text":"can expect a life span of only 30 years."},{"time":261033,"text":"That is less than half of the life span"},{"time":263778,"text":"that its employees can expect to enjoy."}]},{"cues":[{"time":267743,"text":"Now, if you were the CEO\nof such a company,"},{"time":270961,"text":"badgered by investors\nand buffeted by change,"},{"time":274379,"text":"we might forgive you\nfor not even worrying too much"},{"time":276918,"text":"about what happens 30 years out."},{"time":279090,"text":"But here's something that should\nkeep you awake at night:"},{"time":283840,"text":"the probability that your company\nwill not be around in five year's time,"},{"time":287449,"text":"on average, is now\na staggering 32 percent."},{"time":292164,"text":"That's a one in three chance\nthat your company will be taken over"},{"time":296232,"text":"or will fail within just five years."}]},{"cues":[{"time":301696,"text":"Let's come back\nto our tech CEO's question."},{"time":304034,"text":"Where better to turn\nfor advice than nature,"},{"time":307837,"text":"that's been in the business\nof life and death"},{"time":310455,"text":"for longer than any company?"},{"time":315147,"text":"As a lapsed biologist,"},{"time":316954,"text":"I decided to immediately call\na real biologist,"},{"time":320339,"text":"my friend Simon Levin,"},{"time":322377,"text":"Professor of Biology and Mathematics\nat Princeton University."},{"time":326461,"text":"Together, we looked at a variety\nof biological systems,"},{"time":330115,"text":"ranging from natural tropical rainforests"},{"time":333405,"text":"through to managed forests and fisheries."},{"time":336351,"text":"And we asked ourselves the question:"},{"time":338099,"text":"What makes these systems\nresilient and enduring?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":344176,"text":"And what we found\nwas that the same six principles"},{"time":348345,"text":"that we saw underpinning\nthe miracle of the human immune system"},{"time":351394,"text":"actually cropped up again and again,"},{"time":355157,"text":"from redundancy through to embeddedness."},{"time":359129,"text":"In fact, we saw these principles\nnot only in biologically enduring systems,"},{"time":363299,"text":"we also found them\nbeing very characteristic"},{"time":366194,"text":"of long-lived social systems,"},{"time":368605,"text":"like the Roman Empire\nand the Catholic Church,"},{"time":370847,"text":"believe it or not."},{"time":372169,"text":"We also went on to look at business,"},{"time":374031,"text":"and found that these very same properties\nalso characterized businesses"},{"time":378911,"text":"that were resilient and long-lived,"},{"time":380895,"text":"and we noted their absence\nfrom ones which were short-lived."}]},{"cues":[{"time":387162,"text":"Let's first take a look at what happens\nwhen the corporate immune system"},{"time":391208,"text":"collapses."},{"time":393202,"text":"This beautiful building is part\nof the Shitennoji Temple Complex"},{"time":397768,"text":"in Osaka, Japan."},{"time":399672,"text":"In fact, it's one of the oldest\ntemples in Japan."},{"time":403165,"text":"It was built by a Korean artisan,"},{"time":405417,"text":"because at the time,\nJapan was not yet building temples."},{"time":408933,"text":"And this Korean artisan went on\nto found a temple-building company."},{"time":415017,"text":"Amazingly, his company, Kongō Gumi,"},{"time":418446,"text":"was still around 1,428 years later."},{"time":423694,"text":"In fact, it became the oldest\ncontinuously operating company"},{"time":427318,"text":"in the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":429986,"text":"So how is Kongō Gumi doing today?"},{"time":434280,"text":"Not too well, I'm afraid."},{"time":436559,"text":"It borrowed very heavily"},{"time":437936,"text":"during the bubble period\nof the Japanese economy,"},{"time":440738,"text":"to invest in real estate."},{"time":442225,"text":"And when the bubble burst,\nit couldn't refinance its loans."},{"time":446463,"text":"The company failed,"},{"time":447775,"text":"and it was taken over\nby a major construction company."},{"time":452735,"text":"Tragically, after 40 generations\nof very careful stewardship"},{"time":457466,"text":"by the Kongō family,"},{"time":459834,"text":"Kongō Gumi succumbed\nto a spectacular lapse"},{"time":463538,"text":"in the ability to apply\na principle of prudence."}]},{"cues":[{"time":468439,"text":"Speaking of company failures:"},{"time":471552,"text":"we're all familiar\nwith the failure of Kodak,"},{"time":474908,"text":"the company that declared bankruptcy"},{"time":477494,"text":"in January 2012."},{"time":481322,"text":"Much more interesting,\nhowever, is the question:"},{"time":485285,"text":"Why did Fujifilm --"},{"time":487662,"text":"same product, same pressures\nfrom digital technology, same time --"},{"time":492929,"text":"why was Fujifilm\nable to survive and flourish?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":498846,"text":"Fujifilm used its capabilities\nin chemistry, material science and optics"},{"time":505558,"text":"to diversify into a number of areas,"},{"time":508953,"text":"ranging from cosmetics to pharmaceuticals,"},{"time":512025,"text":"to medical systems to biomaterials."},{"time":514035,"text":"Some of these diversification\nattempts failed."},{"time":517900,"text":"But in aggregate,"},{"time":519088,"text":"it was able to adapt\nits portfolio sufficiently"},{"time":523452,"text":"to survive and flourish."},{"time":526633,"text":"As the CEO, Mr. Komori, put it,"},{"time":529500,"text":"the strategy succeeded\nbecause it had \"more pockets and drawers\""},{"time":533760,"text":"than the rivals."},{"time":535175,"text":"He meant, of course,"},{"time":536350,"text":"that they were able to create\nmore options than the rivals."},{"time":541137,"text":"Fujifilm survived because it applied\nthe principles of prudence,"},{"time":545574,"text":"diversity"},{"time":546989,"text":"and adaptation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":549615,"text":"A catastrophic factory fire,\nlike the one we see here,"},{"time":553308,"text":"completely wiped out, in one evening,"},{"time":556880,"text":"the only plant which supplied Toyota\nwith valves for car-braking systems."},{"time":564313,"text":"The ultimate test of resilience."},{"time":568193,"text":"Car production ground\nto a screeching halt."},{"time":572629,"text":"How was it, then, that Toyota\nwas able to recover car production?"},{"time":578261,"text":"Can you imagine how long it took?"},{"time":580208,"text":"Just five days."},{"time":582005,"text":"From having no braking valves\nto complete recovery in five days."},{"time":586966,"text":"How was this possible?"},{"time":588747,"text":"Toyota managed its network of suppliers\nin such a collaborative manner"},{"time":594057,"text":"that it could work very quickly\nand smoothly with suppliers"},{"time":598317,"text":"to repurpose production,"},{"time":601099,"text":"fill the missing braking valve capacity"},{"time":603653,"text":"and have car production come online again."},{"time":608093,"text":"Toyota applied the principles\nof modularity of its supply network,"},{"time":612419,"text":"embeddedness in an integrated system"},{"time":615154,"text":"and the functional redundancy\nto be able to repurpose, smoothly,"},{"time":619214,"text":"existing capacity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":622150,"text":"Now fortunately, few companies\nsuccumb to catastrophic fires."},{"time":627189,"text":"But we do read in the newspaper\nevery day about companies"},{"time":630306,"text":"succumbing to the disruption\nof technology."},{"time":634612,"text":"How is it, then, that the consumer\noptics giant Essilor"},{"time":638558,"text":"is able to avoid technology disruption,\nand even profit from it?"},{"time":643095,"text":"And yes, technology disruption\nis not only a big deal"},{"time":646563,"text":"in software and electronics."},{"time":649917,"text":"Essilor carefully scans\nthe competitive environment"},{"time":654262,"text":"for potentially disruptive technologies."},{"time":657483,"text":"It acquires those technologies very early,"},{"time":660317,"text":"before they've become expensive\nor competitors have mobilized around them,"},{"time":664117,"text":"and it then develops\nthose technologies itself,"},{"time":667297,"text":"even at the risk of failure"},{"time":669263,"text":"or the risk of self-disruption."},{"time":672409,"text":"Essilor stays ahead of its game,"},{"time":675051,"text":"and has delivered spectacular performance"},{"time":677081,"text":"for over 40 years,"},{"time":678548,"text":"by using the principles\nof prudence and adaptation."}]},{"cues":[{"time":683901,"text":"OK, if these principles are so powerful,\nyou might be thinking,"},{"time":687986,"text":"why are they not commonplace in business?"},{"time":690917,"text":"Why do we not use these words every day?"},{"time":693625,"text":"Well, change has to first\nstart in the mind."},{"time":695976,"text":"If we think back to our pitch to Bob,"},{"time":698045,"text":"in order to apply the principles"},{"time":700457,"text":"that underpin the miracle\nof the human immune system,"},{"time":703827,"text":"we first need to think differently"},{"time":706255,"text":"about business."},{"time":707838,"text":"Now typically, when we think\nabout business,"},{"time":710569,"text":"we use what I call \"mechanical thinking.\""},{"time":713962,"text":"We set goals,"},{"time":715623,"text":"we analyze problems,"},{"time":717186,"text":"we construct and we adhere to plans,"},{"time":719537,"text":"and more than anything else,"},{"time":720904,"text":"we stress efficiency\nand short-term performance."},{"time":724333,"text":"Now, don't get me wrong --"},{"time":725618,"text":"this is a splendidly practical\nand effective way"},{"time":728756,"text":"of addressing relatively simple challenges"},{"time":731220,"text":"in relatively stable environments."},{"time":734005,"text":"It's the way that Bob -- and probably\nmany of us, myself included --"},{"time":737491,"text":"process most business problems\nwe're faced with every day."},{"time":741374,"text":"In fact, it was a pretty good\nmental model for business --"},{"time":745036,"text":"overall --"},{"time":746581,"text":"until about the mid-1980s,"},{"time":748633,"text":"when the conjunction of globalization"},{"time":752021,"text":"and a revolution in technology\nand telecommunications"},{"time":754568,"text":"made business far more\ndynamic and unpredictable."}]},{"cues":[{"time":757497,"text":"But what about those more dynamic\nand unpredictable situations"},{"time":760599,"text":"that we now increasingly face?"},{"time":763597,"text":"I think in addition\nto the mechanical thinking,"},{"time":766036,"text":"we now need to master the art\nof biological thinking,"},{"time":770417,"text":"as embodied by our six principles."},{"time":773245,"text":"In other words, we need to think\nmore modestly and subtly"},{"time":776922,"text":"about when and how"},{"time":779242,"text":"we can shape, rather than control,"},{"time":782928,"text":"unpredictable and complex situations."},{"time":787551,"text":"It's a little like the difference\nbetween throwing a ball"},{"time":791403,"text":"and releasing a bird."},{"time":793685,"text":"The ball would head in a straight line,"},{"time":795652,"text":"probably towards the intended target,"},{"time":797894,"text":"and the bird certainly would not."}]},{"cues":[{"time":803455,"text":"So what do you think?"},{"time":805073,"text":"Sounds a little impractical,\na little theoretical, perhaps?"},{"time":809821,"text":"Not at all."},{"time":811657,"text":"Every small entrepreneurial company"},{"time":815038,"text":"naturally thinks and acts biologically."},{"time":818404,"text":"Why?"},{"time":819579,"text":"Because it lacks the resources\nto shape its environment"},{"time":822233,"text":"through brute force."},{"time":823551,"text":"It lacks the scale to buffer change,"},{"time":827254,"text":"and it's constantly thinking\nabout the tough odds"},{"time":830451,"text":"for a start-up to survive."},{"time":834637,"text":"Now, the irony is, of course,"},{"time":836059,"text":"that every large company started off\nas a small, entrepreneurial company."},{"time":839660,"text":"But along the way somewhere,"},{"time":841255,"text":"many have lost this ability\nto think and act biologically."},{"time":846604,"text":"They need to rejuvenate\ntheir ability to think biologically"},{"time":851603,"text":"in order to survive and thrive\nin today's environment."}]},{"cues":[{"time":856704,"text":"So let's not just think\nabout short-term performance."},{"time":860079,"text":"Every company I know spends plenty of time"},{"time":862979,"text":"thinking about the central\nquestion of strategy:"},{"time":865400,"text":"How good is our competitive game?"},{"time":867802,"text":"In addition, let's also consider"},{"time":870168,"text":"the second, more biological\nand equally important question:"},{"time":874253,"text":"How long will that game last?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":877081,"text":"Thank you very much."}]},{"cues":[{"time":878286,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}